task.summary: Added 1D profile code to generate all profiles on one image.
Added example code to find the minimum Vp, Vs, and density (as well as the grid points that those properties are at) within standard EL text-based models.
Added example code to find various depth profiles for CVM-S4.26, as well as pulling the raw data.
Added example code to generate text horizontal slices at multiple depths with one or more models. Utilizes the old PyCVM Python interface.
Added code to find the minimum and maximum Vp/Vs ratio within the CCA model in UCVM 15.10.0.
Fixed bug in poisson ratio code.
Fixed small bug in metadata output.
Added scripts to check on ratios from original dataset and find ratios below 1.6.
Fixed bug with extract horizontal slice script.
